==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Raking
<hw>Rak"ing</hw> <pr>(r⟦amac⟧k"⟦icr⟧ng)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The act or process of using a rake; the going over a space with a
rake.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A space gone over with a rake; also, the work done,
or the quantity of hay, grain, etc., collected, by going once over a
space with a rake.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rakish</ent>⟦br⟧
